have justice. Economic justice, racial justice,

04:27.200 --> 04:33.120
environmental justice—any form of “social”
justice which seeks to “correct” actual

04:33.120 --> 04:39.300
justice—undermines破坏，暗中破坏 justice.
So, then, if social justice is not a biblical

04:39.300 --> 04:43.960
concept, why do so many churches and synagogues犹太教会堂
promote it?

04:43.960 --> 04:49.740
Because many Christians and Jews no longer
regard biblical principles as binding有约束力的. Because

04:49.740 --> 04:54.710
it’s a lot easier to dispense分发 compassion同情，怜悯
than hold people to a biblical standard. And

04:54.710 --> 05:00.750
